00:41:49.270 --> 00:41:50.680 align:middle line:84%
There are different
types of mantras,

00:41:50.680 --> 00:41:55.420 align:middle line:84%
but a transcending mantra, to
take you to the transcendent,

00:41:55.420 --> 00:41:57.050 align:middle line:90%
has a special property.

00:41:57.050 --> 00:41:59.350 align:middle line:84%
It is a sound that
is experienced

00:41:59.350 --> 00:42:03.960 align:middle line:84%
